<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="II">ORDER</TI>
<P>THIS APPEAL FROM THE DECISION OF Master Short was heard on February 26, 2018 and reasons were released on April 4, 2018.</P>
<P>ON READING the Appeal Book and Compendium, Facta and Book of Authorities filed on behalf of the parties and on hearing submissions by counsel for the parties;</P>
<P>1. THIS COURT ORDERS that the appeal of the Plaintiff is dismissed pursuant to the reasons of Justice Wilson.</P>
<P>2. THIS COURT ORDERS that the plaintiffs shall pay to the defendant costs fixed in the amount of $6,000.00.</P>
<P>&ellip35; MAY 14 2018</P>
<P>R. Ittleman, Registrar</P>
